body: @jreback The idea of the Mixin makes sense. Took me a bit to wrap my head around it. I had to add `self.engine` to a couple of the tests because `bzip` decompression will not raise an exception and so the Compression Mixin needs to check what engine it is using to make sure the test runs correctly.
@jreback I think this is ready for your review.

Jeff is going to ask you to squash your commits into one, as per the contributing docs.
Nice job overall!
